{"tid":609510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門呢個地方真係幾撚好笑","createTime":"2018-03-29T06:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T14:16:34.000Z","uid":34149,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aea4a0baffca438b966243a99416b80915f612df","tid":609510,"uid":34149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"天宮一號料周末墜落地球 不構成危險<br />\n<br />\n【澳門日報消息】綜合消息：據預測，中國天宮一號空間站將在復活節長周末墜落地球，不過不會對人類安全造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n中國天宮一號空間站於2011年發射升空，於2016年正式停止使用。自停止使用以來，該空間站的高度一直在穩步下降，現在看來它將脫離軌道，在復活節長周末撞擊地球。<br />\n<br />\n目前該航天器每一個半小時環繞地球飛行一圈，速度為每小時2.8萬公里，其軌跡在南北緯43度之間。這使澳大利亞、非洲、南美洲、美國大部分地區以及東南亞都處在可能的撞擊區內。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲航天局說，中國天宮一號太空實驗室可能在3月30日和4月2日之間墜落地球，殘骸碎片撒落範圍可達數千平方公里，不過對人構成的危險非常小。這個長10.4米的空間站預計將在南北緯43度之間的某個點再入地球大氣層。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://h5.newaircloud.com/news_detail?newsid=3403648_aomen&amp;app=1&amp;from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fh5.newaircloud.com%2Fnews_detail%3Fnewsid%3D3403648_aomen%26app%3D1%26from%3Dtimeline%26isappinstalled%3D0&d=COf4k7jTPEmF4XvtUefdGBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5e14ae0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://h5.newaircloud.com/news_detail?newsid=3403648_aomen&amp;app=1&amp;from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0</a><br />\n<br />\n學過自由落體都知有乜可能無危險 澳門真係一塊樂土"},{"pid":"80dd3b3a12e57079a276c3720bd76e472fe1ec54","tid":609510,"uid":177089,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/29/141212_e8df6ef789754df2086135e9687e2835.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2F141212_e8df6ef789754df2086135e9687e2835.jpeg&h=8b0e17bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9c818c27024a6237cfdbd4763f3a6a1ef25c0ee","tid":609510,"uid":81743,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:14:13.000Z","msg":"係報紙公司好笑定係澳門人好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=